snippet.title: Cosmic Arcade Tycoon - Steam Next Fest: February 2025 Demo
snippet.description:
Build your dream arcade at your own pace. No pressure, no deadlines, just a cozy space to fill with games, decorations, and warm neon lights.

This isn’t about maximizing profits or building an empire. It’s about creativity, nostalgia, and the simple joy of crafting the perfect arcade, one machine at a time.

Developed by NebulaNookGames
Release Date: March 6th, 2025

#steam #steamgames #steamgame #theforeseenarcade #steamnextfest #steamnextfestfebruary2025 #cosmicarcadetycoon
